article:
The following outline is provided as an overview of and topical guide to the
United Kingdom:

The 'United Kingdom of Great Britain and Northern Ireland', commonly known as
the 'United Kingdom', the 'UK', or 'Britain', is a sovereign island nation
located in the British Isles of Western Europe. The United Kingdom
comprises the island of Great Britain, the northeastern part of the island of
Ireland, and a large number of smaller islands.
